WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 34=

00:01:49.490 --> 00:01:50.330 line:80%
Zhao.

00:01:50.820 --> 00:01:51.660 line:80%
Zhao?

00:01:57.850 --> 00:01:59.210 line:80%
You've slept for days.

00:01:59.930 --> 00:02:01.180 line:80%
If I hadn't come,

00:02:03.060 --> 00:02:04.090 line:80%
you would be dead.

00:02:14.210 --> 00:02:15.780 line:80%
That man in black is strong.

00:02:17.020 --> 00:02:18.300 line:80%
How did you escape?

00:02:19.210 --> 00:02:20.210 line:80%
I have my ways.

00:02:22.780 --> 00:02:23.620 line:80%
Here.

00:02:24.090 --> 00:02:24.930 line:80%
Take medicine.

00:02:43.810 --> 00:02:45.020 line:80%
Smiley.

00:02:45.620 --> 00:02:46.530 line:80%
Not as good as yours.

00:02:47.410 --> 00:02:48.460 line:80%
Just make do.

00:03:01.970 --> 00:03:02.810 line:80%
Zhao,

00:03:05.580 --> 00:03:07.740 line:80%
the man in black

00:03:09.620 --> 00:03:10.810 line:80%
feels like someone I know.

00:03:14.060 --> 00:03:14.900 line:80%
Lord Qi.

00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:21.970 line:80%
No.

00:03:21.970 --> 00:03:22.930 line:80%
It can't be Master.

00:03:24.060 --> 00:03:24.900 line:80%
It's Li Wenxun.

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:32.210 line:80%
Where are the others?

00:03:32.896 --> 00:03:34.580 line:80%
The Abbess brought
the surviving disciples

00:03:34.580 --> 00:03:36.210 line:80%
to a safe place.

00:03:36.810 --> 00:03:38.180 line:80%
Song Yuzhi and Fan Xingjia

00:03:38.180 --> 00:03:39.490 line:80%
returned to Qingque Town.

00:03:41.060 --> 00:03:42.860 line:80%
They took the Jade Sunflower.

00:03:43.340 --> 00:03:44.650 line:80%
They also used Xingjia

00:03:44.650 --> 00:03:45.690 line:80%
to take the Night Orchid.

00:03:46.780 --> 00:03:47.620 line:80%
Now,

00:03:47.970 --> 00:03:50.060 line:80%
with both the treasures,

00:03:50.650 --> 00:03:52.090 line:80%
he will cultivate.

00:03:52.410 --> 00:03:53.930 line:80%
If he masters the Ziwei Method,

00:03:54.460 --> 00:03:56.020 line:80%
he will be the next Nie Hengcheng.

00:03:56.530 --> 00:03:57.370 line:80%
No.

00:03:57.970 --> 00:03:59.690 line:80%
We can't let

00:03:59.690 --> 00:04:00.620 line:80%
the tragedy repeat.

00:04:02.210 --> 00:04:04.090 line:80%
Are you going to risk your life
like your aunt?

00:04:04.090 --> 00:04:05.210 line:80%
That's my choice.

00:04:06.650 --> 00:04:07.530 line:80%
If I don't die,

00:04:08.740 --> 00:04:09.930 line:80%
I'll repay

00:04:11.370 --> 00:04:12.620 line:80%
today's life-saving favor.

00:04:14.810 --> 00:04:15.650 line:80%
Let me go.

00:04:19.850 --> 00:04:20.690 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:04:24.290 --> 00:04:25.820 line:80%
I've stayed up several nights

00:04:25.820 --> 00:04:26.970 line:80%
for an ingrate.

00:04:28.460 --> 00:04:29.460 line:80%
I'm a little tired.

00:04:37.730 --> 00:04:38.570 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:39.460 --> 00:04:41.290 line:80%
there won't be another Nie Hengcheng.

00:04:43.460 --> 00:04:45.500 line:80%
He won't be able to master
the Ziwei Method.

00:04:52.090 --> 00:04:53.940 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang is buried here.

00:04:54.700 --> 00:04:55.820 line:80%
You found the body?

00:04:56.340 --> 00:04:57.900 line:80%
When reorganizing Bliss Palace,

00:04:58.410 --> 00:04:59.900 line:80%
we found a corpse in a stone cave

00:05:00.410 --> 00:05:01.610 line:80%
near the underground palace.

00:05:01.762 --> 00:05:04.265 line:80%
The fatal wound runs
from the left shoulder to the right rib.

00:05:04.410 --> 00:05:05.380 line:80%
The sternum is broken.

00:05:05.970 --> 00:05:06.810 line:80%
It's a blade wound.

00:05:07.340 --> 00:05:08.380 line:80%
The Sunshine Blade.

00:05:10.543 --> 00:05:11.652 line:80%
Ms. Cai must have chased him

00:05:11.663 --> 00:05:12.970 line:80%
all the way near Bliss Palace,

00:05:13.970 --> 00:05:15.380 line:80%
cornered Mu Zhengyang,

00:05:15.970 --> 00:05:17.140 line:80%
and killed him on the spot.

00:05:18.090 --> 00:05:19.056 line:80%
As for why Nie Hengcheng

00:05:19.067 --> 00:05:20.650 line:80%
failed to master the Ziwei Method,

00:05:21.140 --> 00:05:22.380 line:80%
the answer lies within.

00:05:25.340 --> 00:05:27.260 line:80%
(Zhengyang)

00:05:27.730 --> 00:05:29.020 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang's handbook?

00:05:31.780 --> 00:05:33.170 line:80%
(Nie is treacherous.)

00:05:33.940 --> 00:05:35.620 line:80%
(After torturing me
with a branding iron,)

00:05:35.700 --> 00:05:36.940 line:80%
(he still wanted to kill me.)

00:05:36.940 --> 00:05:37.900 line:80%
(Jiuzhou Archive)

00:05:37.900 --> 00:05:39.290 line:80%
(My brother hid me)

00:05:39.940 --> 00:05:41.530 line:80%
(in the Jiuzhou Archive.)

00:05:42.460 --> 00:05:43.300 line:80%
(I got bored)

00:05:43.700 --> 00:05:44.700 line:80%
(and read all the books.)

00:05:45.210 --> 00:05:47.290 line:80%
(Unexpectedly, I found
the ancient Ziwei Method.)

00:05:49.970 --> 00:05:50.810 line:80%
(It's said)

00:05:51.009 --> 00:05:52.965 line:80%
(that the Founder's son wanted
to practice this,)

00:05:53.050 --> 00:05:54.580 line:80%
(but he was forbidden.)

00:05:56.410 --> 00:05:58.140 line:80%
(This method requires the life force)

00:05:58.970 --> 00:06:00.700 line:80%
(of a close relative.)

00:06:01.650 --> 00:06:03.410 line:80%
(Otherwise, one goes mad)

00:06:03.410 --> 00:06:04.460 line:80%
(and dies.)

00:06:06.050 --> 00:06:07.380 line:80%
(To avenge past shame,)

00:06:08.340 --> 00:06:09.700 line:80%
(I lured Nie Hengcheng)

00:06:10.290 --> 00:06:11.530 line:80%
(to practice the Ziwei Method.)

00:06:12.940 --> 00:06:14.290 line:80%
(But the necessary saliva)

00:06:14.970 --> 00:06:16.530 line:80%
(and the Night Orchid)

00:06:17.650 --> 00:06:19.780 line:80%
(are connected
to the Luoying demoness.)

00:06:20.780 --> 00:06:21.620 line:80%
(So,)

00:06:22.900 --> 00:06:24.780 line:80%
(I deliberately approached Pingshu.)

00:06:28.700 --> 00:06:29.540 line:80%
(Later,)

00:06:30.610 --> 00:06:32.530 line:80%
(Pingshu's friends, the Shi brothers,)

00:06:32.530 --> 00:06:33.970 line:80%
(were poisoned by the Nether Aura.)

00:06:34.780 --> 00:06:37.210 line:80%
(They urgently needed
the Jade Sunflower.)

00:06:38.170 --> 00:06:39.650 line:80%
(I told her my identity)

00:06:40.340 --> 00:06:41.850 line:80%
(and stole it for her)

00:06:42.580 --> 00:06:43.900 line:80%
(to gain her trust.)

00:06:45.730 --> 00:06:47.140 line:80%
You'll kill Nie Hengcheng?

00:06:47.650 --> 00:06:48.900 line:80%
As long as I get the saliva,

00:06:49.290 --> 00:06:50.256 line:80%
I can increase my power,

00:06:50.850 --> 00:06:52.140 line:80%
kill Nie Hengcheng,

00:06:52.140 --> 00:06:53.090 line:80%
and reclaim the Li Sect.

00:06:53.820 --> 00:06:54.780 line:80%
At that time,

00:06:54.780 --> 00:06:56.290 line:80%
the Six Sects and Li Sect

00:06:56.290 --> 00:06:57.780 line:80%
will lay down arms

00:06:58.820 --> 00:06:59.700 line:80%
and restore peace

00:07:00.500 --> 00:07:01.700 line:80%
to Jianghu.

00:07:08.780 --> 00:07:09.780 line:80%
The saliva is

00:07:10.730 --> 00:07:11.616 line:80%
in the snow mountains.

00:07:32.170 --> 00:07:33.900 line:80%
♪In days gone by♪

00:07:34.210 --> 00:07:35.760 line:80%
♪Willows swayed gently♪

00:07:36.060 --> 00:07:38.810 line:80%
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

00:07:39.780 --> 00:07:40.970 line:80%
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

00:07:40.980 --> 00:07:42.450 line:80%
♪A fleeting glance♪

00:07:42.620 --> 00:07:43.530 line:80%
♪And then♪

00:07:43.540 --> 00:07:46.490 line:80%
♪Love consumed me♪

00:07:47.300 --> 00:07:48.850 line:80%
♪Now I think of you♪

00:07:49.250 --> 00:07:50.890 line:80%
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

00:07:51.150 --> 00:07:52.490 line:80%
♪Alas, we parted♪

00:07:52.500 --> 00:07:54.690 line:80%
♪Longing for your return♪

00:07:54.820 --> 00:07:55.770 line:80%
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

00:07:55.780 --> 00:07:57.250 line:80%
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

00:07:57.260 --> 00:07:58.290 line:80%
♪Scattered petals♪

00:07:58.300 --> 00:08:00.530 line:80%
♪Cover the ground♪

00:08:01.390 --> 00:08:03.850 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:08:05.900 --> 00:08:08.700 line:80%
Irises will bring you luck.

00:08:08.730 --> 00:08:11.450 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:08:11.710 --> 00:08:15.650 line:80%
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

00:08:16.370 --> 00:08:18.900 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:08:19.180 --> 00:08:23.430 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:08:24.500 --> 00:08:25.900 line:80%
It's the irises.

00:08:25.900 --> 00:08:27.120 line:80%
They'll bring you luck.

00:08:27.130 --> 00:08:31.030 line:80%
♪Tears are like pearls♪

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:49.530 line:80%
♪Things stay, yet you're away♪

00:08:49.910 --> 00:08:54.130 line:80%
♪Who will hear the broken strings♪

00:08:54.670 --> 00:08:56.770 line:80%
♪Across the starry skies♪

00:08:57.150 --> 00:09:02.030 line:80%
♪I see your shadow there♪

00:09:02.190 --> 00:09:04.970 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:09:04.970 --> 00:09:09.450 line:80%
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

00:09:09.700 --> 00:09:12.310 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:09:12.520 --> 00:09:16.620 line:80%
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

00:09:17.650 --> 00:09:18.490 line:80%
(Later,)

00:09:19.330 --> 00:09:20.780 line:80%
(I roamed Jianghu with her.)

00:09:21.500 --> 00:09:22.530 line:80%
(She accompanied me)

00:09:22.530 --> 00:09:23.900 line:80%
(to find the Night Orchid.)

00:09:25.220 --> 00:09:26.500 line:80%
(I enjoyed)

00:09:27.100 --> 00:09:28.690 line:80%
(my comfortable time with her.)

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:38.350 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:09:38.780 --> 00:09:42.030 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:09:43.530 --> 00:09:44.530 line:80%
Master Zhengyang,

00:09:44.900 --> 00:09:47.650 line:80%
feelings should be expressed.

00:10:02.450 --> 00:10:04.220 line:80%
(If not for the unresolved feud,)

00:10:05.810 --> 00:10:07.650 line:80%
(I'd want to be with her forever.)

00:10:28.930 --> 00:10:29.980 line:80%
(As expected,)

00:10:30.983 --> 00:10:32.100 line:80%
(Nie Hengcheng lost control)

00:10:32.100 --> 00:10:33.780 line:80%
(after reaching the third level)

00:10:34.450 --> 00:10:35.356 line:80%
(of the Ziwei Method,)

00:10:36.140 --> 00:10:37.500 line:80%
(harming martial artists.)

00:10:39.380 --> 00:10:41.620 line:80%
(Yin Dai of Qingque Sect
led a battle against him.)

00:10:42.690 --> 00:10:44.450 line:80%
(I intended to benefit from it.)

00:10:45.410 --> 00:10:46.250 line:80%
(Unexpectedly,)

00:10:46.410 --> 00:10:47.650 line:80%
(Pingshu, a junior,)

00:10:47.980 --> 00:10:49.240 line:80%
(together with several friends)

00:10:49.980 --> 00:10:51.900 line:80%
(improved the Big Dipper Formation,)

00:10:52.690 --> 00:10:54.690 line:80%
(planning to use it to kill Nie.)

00:10:56.980 --> 00:10:58.570 line:80%
Must you go to kill him now?

00:10:58.570 --> 00:10:59.900 line:80%
Nie's crimes are unforgivable.

00:11:00.900 --> 00:11:02.500 line:80%
Even if it costs my life,

00:11:02.500 --> 00:11:03.386 line:80%
he must be eliminated.

00:11:05.900 --> 00:11:07.100 line:80%
Since you've decided,

00:11:08.140 --> 00:11:08.980 line:80%
I'll accompany you.

00:11:10.330 --> 00:11:11.450 line:80%
But before that,

00:11:13.780 --> 00:11:14.780 line:80%
let's get married.

00:11:18.290 --> 00:11:19.130 line:80%
Okay.

00:11:25.500 --> 00:11:26.650 line:80%
(We made marriage vows)

00:11:27.380 --> 00:11:28.530 line:80%
(and bound our love.)

00:11:30.020 --> 00:11:32.410 line:80%
(I also learned the whereabouts
of Pingshu's friends)

00:11:34.220 --> 00:11:35.740 line:80%
(and planned an ambush for them.)

00:11:42.690 --> 00:11:44.380 line:80%
He intended to kill Nie Hengcheng,

00:11:45.570 --> 00:11:47.100 line:80%
so why harm my aunt's friends?

00:11:47.780 --> 00:11:48.690 line:80%
For power.

00:11:49.020 --> 00:11:50.170 line:80%
For sole rule over the world.

00:11:50.620 --> 00:11:51.460 line:80%
At that time,

00:11:51.690 --> 00:11:53.100 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng was going mad.

00:11:53.410 --> 00:11:54.380 line:80%
He was near death.

00:11:54.380 --> 00:11:55.860 line:80%
My father wouldn't contest.

00:11:56.410 --> 00:11:58.900 line:80%
He only needed
to eliminate Nie's remnants

00:11:59.530 --> 00:12:01.500 line:80%
to become the Chief.

00:12:01.500 --> 00:12:03.066 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang feared no one like Yin Dai,

00:12:03.620 --> 00:12:05.410 line:80%
but he feared your aunt

00:12:05.410 --> 00:12:07.140 line:80%
and her friends.

00:12:07.620 --> 00:12:09.050 line:80%
They were top-tier martial artists.

00:12:09.650 --> 00:12:11.380 line:80%
If they formed
a seven-person sword array,

00:12:11.690 --> 00:12:12.690 line:80%
how could he resist?

00:12:13.050 --> 00:12:14.620 line:80%
So, he killed them early.

00:12:15.290 --> 00:12:16.650 line:80%
But he never expected

00:12:17.570 --> 00:12:19.450 line:80%
Lu Chengnan to betray the sect.

00:12:19.900 --> 00:12:21.570 line:80%
After being gravely injured,

00:12:21.570 --> 00:12:22.863 line:80%
Lu Chengnan escaped to Chang Fort

00:12:23.570 --> 00:12:24.810 line:80%
and revealed the Ziwei Method

00:12:24.810 --> 00:12:27.140 line:80%
and Nie Hengcheng's secrets to my aunt.

00:12:29.530 --> 00:12:31.380 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang lost everything.

00:12:31.860 --> 00:12:32.700 line:80%
Indeed.

00:12:33.100 --> 00:12:34.690 line:80%
My aunt must have been heartbroken

00:12:36.860 --> 00:12:38.100 line:80%
upon learning the truth.

00:13:51.250 --> 00:13:54.960 line:80%
♪Life♪

00:13:54.970 --> 00:13:57.390 line:80%
♪Passes swiftly♪

00:13:58.180 --> 00:14:00.070 line:80%
♪Time is long♪

00:14:00.080 --> 00:14:01.820 line:80%
♪Pleasures are few♪

00:14:01.830 --> 00:14:05.630 line:80%
♪Too many days lost♪

00:14:05.650 --> 00:14:09.820 line:80%
♪How many lovers♪

00:14:09.830 --> 00:14:13.360 line:80%
♪Once stood side by side
through hardships♪

00:14:13.420 --> 00:14:14.940 line:80%
♪In the end♪

00:14:14.950 --> 00:14:19.940 line:80%
♪They forget each other♪

00:14:19.940 --> 00:14:22.920 line:80%
♪Fate♪

00:14:23.140 --> 00:14:26.610 line:80%
♪Passes swiftly♪

00:14:26.780 --> 00:14:28.730 line:80%
♪Liquor is strong♪

00:14:28.740 --> 00:14:30.720 line:80%
♪Chests are warm♪

00:14:30.730 --> 00:14:34.570 line:80%
♪Loyalty turns cold♪

00:14:34.570 --> 00:14:40.030 line:80%
♪Many affections are hard to sever♪

00:14:40.510 --> 00:14:44.150 line:80%
♪Leaving only me♪

00:14:46.050 --> 00:14:47.650 line:80%
(I don't regret what I did.)

00:14:49.450 --> 00:14:50.860 line:80%
(I only feel indebted)

00:14:52.100 --> 00:14:53.220 line:80%
(to Zhengming and Pingshu.)

00:14:56.170 --> 00:14:57.170 line:80%
(In fact, Nie Hengcheng)

00:14:57.620 --> 00:14:58.650 line:80%
(didn't know that mastery)

00:14:58.650 --> 00:15:01.450 line:80%
(requires a relative's life force,)

00:15:01.450 --> 00:15:03.220 line:80%
(so he'd die within three years.)

00:15:03.930 --> 00:15:05.220 line:80%
(But Pingshu's temperament)

00:15:06.170 --> 00:15:07.530 line:80%
(won't allow her to wait.)

00:15:10.100 --> 00:15:11.220 line:80%
(Perhaps one day,)

00:15:12.410 --> 00:15:14.140 line:80%
(I can apologize to her
in the underworld.)

00:15:26.810 --> 00:15:27.860 line:80%
A relative's life force?

00:15:28.650 --> 00:15:29.740 line:80%
The Ziwei Method,

00:15:30.170 --> 00:15:31.050 line:80%
dragon beast saliva,

00:15:31.380 --> 00:15:32.220 line:80%
the Night Orchid,

00:15:32.450 --> 00:15:33.500 line:80%
and the Jade Sunflower

00:15:33.500 --> 00:15:34.570 line:80%
are all indispensable.

00:15:35.100 --> 00:15:36.140 line:80%
The final step requires

00:15:37.570 --> 00:15:38.930 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower

00:15:38.930 --> 00:15:40.530 line:80%
to absorb bloodline energy.

00:15:41.980 --> 00:15:43.650 line:80%
Without it, one goes mad and dies.

00:15:44.860 --> 00:15:45.980 line:80%
This is why the Founder

00:15:45.980 --> 00:15:46.930 line:80%
forbade the Ziwei Method

00:15:46.930 --> 00:15:48.500 line:80%
from spreading,

00:15:49.740 --> 00:15:50.690 line:80%
and the secret

00:15:51.330 --> 00:15:52.283 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang discovered.

00:15:54.100 --> 00:15:54.940 line:80%
Zhao,

00:15:55.410 --> 00:15:56.930 line:80%
my father was once injured

00:15:58.570 --> 00:16:00.100 line:80%
by Mu Zhengyang

00:16:00.100 --> 00:16:01.500 line:80%
because he tried to seize me

00:16:01.500 --> 00:16:03.100 line:80%
as an infant.

00:16:03.100 --> 00:16:04.410 line:80%
I never understood

00:16:04.780 --> 00:16:05.780 line:80%
why he'd do this

00:16:06.410 --> 00:16:08.170 line:80%
until I found his handbook.

00:16:08.170 --> 00:16:09.450 line:80%
I was the one

00:16:10.330 --> 00:16:12.290 line:80%
he had been targeting as close kin.

00:16:14.170 --> 00:16:15.500 line:80%
If the man in black

00:16:15.860 --> 00:16:17.050 line:80%
doesn't know the final step,

00:16:18.100 --> 00:16:19.810 line:80%
he'll go mad and die

00:16:20.220 --> 00:16:21.100 line:80%
like Nie Hengcheng.

00:16:21.780 --> 00:16:22.620 line:80%
Yes.

00:16:23.500 --> 00:16:24.620 line:80%
What we need now

00:16:25.740 --> 00:16:26.690 line:80%
is to wait.

00:16:27.740 --> 00:16:28.620 line:80%
Wait?

00:16:30.356 --> 00:16:32.662 line:80%
Wait for him to go on a killing spree
like Nie Hengcheng?

00:16:34.690 --> 00:16:35.810 line:80%
Do you know why

00:16:36.380 --> 00:16:37.220 line:80%
my aunt,

00:16:37.900 --> 00:16:39.860 line:80%
knowing Nie Hengcheng would die,

00:16:40.330 --> 00:16:42.220 line:80%
still went to Mount Tu to kill him?

00:16:43.050 --> 00:16:43.890 line:80%
Zhao.

00:16:44.050 --> 00:16:44.900 line:80%
Aunt once said,

00:16:45.410 --> 00:16:47.020 line:80%
"There are two kinds of evil people."

00:16:47.840 --> 00:16:48.690 line:80%
"One is the one"

00:16:48.690 --> 00:16:49.690 line:80%
"who commits evil."

00:16:50.100 --> 00:16:50.973 line:80%
"The other is the one"

00:16:51.980 --> 00:16:53.780 line:80%
"who stands by and watches."

00:16:54.860 --> 00:16:56.780 line:80%
I may not be a great heroine
like my aunt,

00:16:58.020 --> 00:16:59.450 line:80%
but I can't stand aside.

00:17:00.050 --> 00:17:01.530 line:80%
Turning a blind eye for a moment

00:17:01.530 --> 00:17:03.290 line:80%
will only bring a lifetime of unrest.

00:17:04.370 --> 00:17:05.610 line:80%
This deal can't be done.

00:17:16.850 --> 00:17:17.690 line:80%
Zhao,

00:17:18.810 --> 00:17:20.810 line:80%
he's reached the third level.

00:17:21.570 --> 00:17:22.660 line:80%
You can't beat him.

00:17:23.130 --> 00:17:24.290 line:80%
So what?

00:17:26.810 --> 00:17:28.180 line:80%
Chivalry requires

00:17:28.180 --> 00:17:30.090 line:80%
attempting the impossible,

00:17:31.420 --> 00:17:32.260 line:80%
right?

00:17:35.180 --> 00:17:36.020 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:17:36.980 --> 00:17:37.890 line:80%
don't stop me.

00:17:39.180 --> 00:17:40.570 line:80%
I don't want us to end up

00:17:41.740 --> 00:17:45.050 line:80%
like Mu Zhengyang and my aunt.

00:18:13.460 --> 00:18:14.300 line:80%
Aunt,

00:18:15.370 --> 00:18:18.420 line:80%
was the Founder really a disciple
of an immortal?

00:18:21.890 --> 00:18:23.420 line:80%
That was centuries ago.

00:18:23.890 --> 00:18:25.460 line:80%
I don't know if it's true.

00:18:26.700 --> 00:18:28.740 line:80%
But as disciples of the Beichen lineage,

00:18:29.370 --> 00:18:31.500 line:80%
we have to give the Founder some honor.

00:18:32.130 --> 00:18:34.530 line:80%
Do you want it to be true or false?

00:18:34.530 --> 00:18:35.980 line:80%
I hope it's false.

00:18:36.530 --> 00:18:37.370 line:80%
Why?

00:18:37.370 --> 00:18:39.890 line:80%
All the other immortals flew to heaven,

00:18:39.890 --> 00:18:43.780 line:80%
leaving only the Founder
in the mortal world.

00:18:43.780 --> 00:18:45.530 line:80%
He must've been pitiful.

00:18:45.530 --> 00:18:47.530 line:80%
You're too kindhearted

00:18:47.530 --> 00:18:49.700 line:80%
to roam Jianghu in the future.

00:19:23.610 --> 00:19:24.450 line:80%
Young Master!

00:19:25.890 --> 00:19:26.730 line:80%
Young Master.

00:19:37.020 --> 00:19:37.890 line:80%
Young Master,

00:19:38.420 --> 00:19:39.530 line:80%
this kind of medicine

00:19:39.530 --> 00:19:41.220 line:80%
is just a desperate, harmful cure.

00:19:41.220 --> 00:19:42.460 line:80%
You can't take it.

00:19:43.500 --> 00:19:44.340 line:80%
It's fine.

00:19:45.660 --> 00:19:47.220 line:80%
I don't have much time anyway.

00:19:48.130 --> 00:19:49.850 line:80%
I could've thought of other ways,

00:19:50.500 --> 00:19:52.130 line:80%
but you insist...

00:19:52.130 --> 00:19:53.050 line:80%
Alright, Uncle Cheng.

00:19:56.370 --> 00:19:57.740 line:80%
I won't die

00:19:59.460 --> 00:20:00.660 line:80%
without seeing the end.

00:20:06.810 --> 00:20:07.650 line:80%
Young Master.

00:20:19.180 --> 00:20:20.220 line:80%
Zhuang?

00:20:20.660 --> 00:20:21.700 line:80%
Today, you'll come with me.

00:20:21.700 --> 00:20:22.540 line:80%
Okay.

00:20:24.660 --> 00:20:25.500 line:80%
Zhao.

00:20:33.460 --> 00:20:34.820 line:80%
- Xingjia.
- Zhao.

00:20:36.220 --> 00:20:37.730 line:80%
Xingjia, sit.

00:20:37.940 --> 00:20:38.810 line:80%
How's your leg?

00:20:38.810 --> 00:20:40.330 line:80%
I'm fine, Zhao.

00:20:40.330 --> 00:20:41.810 line:80%
It's great to see you back safely.

00:20:42.570 --> 00:20:44.130 line:80%
Where is Abbess Jingyuan? How is she?

00:20:44.130 --> 00:20:45.090 line:80%
She's badly injured

00:20:45.090 --> 00:20:46.149 line:80%
but not in mortal danger.

00:20:46.160 --> 00:20:47.573 line:80%
She's been taken care of to recover.

00:20:47.890 --> 00:20:49.740 line:80%
We've sent messages to all sects.

00:20:49.740 --> 00:20:52.180 line:80%
Lord Cai and the others
should arrive soon.

00:20:55.570 --> 00:20:56.660 line:80%
Zhao,

00:20:56.660 --> 00:20:58.043 line:80%
the people who attacked us

00:20:58.054 --> 00:20:59.800 line:80%
- at Xuankong Nunnery...
- Uncle Li, right?

00:21:03.460 --> 00:21:04.300 line:80%
Zhao,

00:21:04.740 --> 00:21:06.420 line:80%
the man in black really was Uncle Li?

00:21:06.980 --> 00:21:08.729 line:80%
He said he had a headache,

00:21:08.740 --> 00:21:10.180 line:80%
so I gave him the remaining essence

00:21:10.180 --> 00:21:11.180 line:80%
to treat it.

00:21:11.500 --> 00:21:12.700 line:80%
I didn't know.

00:21:13.130 --> 00:21:14.220 line:80%
I really didn't know.

00:21:15.610 --> 00:21:16.530 line:80%
I suspect

00:21:16.850 --> 00:21:18.940 line:80%
Master has been deceived by Uncle Li.

00:21:19.610 --> 00:21:21.050 line:80%
Now, Qingque Town is full

00:21:21.050 --> 00:21:22.570 line:80%
of Siqi and Guangtian members.

00:21:22.570 --> 00:21:25.020 line:80%
Yang Heying and Song Xiuzhi
have climbed the mountain,

00:21:25.020 --> 00:21:26.356 line:80%
blaming everything on Mu Qingyan,

00:21:26.367 --> 00:21:28.366 line:80%
and claiming the demonic sect
is about to attack.

00:21:28.377 --> 00:21:29.217 line:80%
Qingque Sect

00:21:29.810 --> 00:21:30.980 line:80%
is now on high alert.

00:21:31.290 --> 00:21:32.500 line:80%
These thugs

00:21:32.850 --> 00:21:33.810 line:80%
always twist the truth.

00:21:34.130 --> 00:21:34.970 line:80%
Zhao,

00:21:35.290 --> 00:21:36.420 line:80%
with the situation so tense,

00:21:36.420 --> 00:21:37.780 line:80%
should we ask Mr. Mu for help?

00:21:40.890 --> 00:21:41.956 line:80%
We should solve the problem

00:21:42.740 --> 00:21:44.050 line:80%
of the Six Sects ourselves.

00:21:45.810 --> 00:21:46.650 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:21:46.850 --> 00:21:48.020 line:80%
we'll climb the mountain

00:21:48.660 --> 00:21:49.600 line:80%
to find Master tonight.

00:22:00.463 --> 00:22:01.420 line:80%
The iron chain mechanism

00:22:01.420 --> 00:22:03.050 line:80%
is usually guarded by trusted disciples.

00:22:03.476 --> 00:22:04.862 line:80%
How could it be left to outsiders?

00:22:05.660 --> 00:22:06.530 line:80%
It seems Fengchi

00:22:06.850 --> 00:22:07.690 line:80%
and Zhuo

00:22:08.570 --> 00:22:09.940 line:80%
have been controlled by Uncle Li.

00:22:15.545 --> 00:22:17.058 line:80%
(Pillar of Jianghu)
What demonic sect?

00:22:17.420 --> 00:22:20.130 line:80%
Yang Heying made the corpse slaves.

00:22:20.130 --> 00:22:20.970 line:80%
You...

00:22:21.890 --> 00:22:23.810 line:80%
You've been deceived too?

00:22:27.380 --> 00:22:31.620 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:22:51.330 --> 00:22:52.170 line:80%
You...

00:22:52.460 --> 00:22:53.420 line:80%
Why are you doing this?

00:23:03.180 --> 00:23:04.020 line:80%
- Master!
- Master!

00:23:06.020 --> 00:23:06.860 line:80%
Zhao,

00:23:07.180 --> 00:23:08.020 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:23:08.700 --> 00:23:09.540 line:80%
why are you here?

00:23:10.610 --> 00:23:12.050 line:80%
I've been worried about you.

00:23:14.850 --> 00:23:16.090 line:80%
Master,

00:23:18.370 --> 00:23:19.660 line:80%
what are you doing?

00:23:24.570 --> 00:23:25.700 line:80%
Why?

00:23:29.740 --> 00:23:30.810 line:80%
I'm only doing this

00:23:32.420 --> 00:23:34.050 line:80%
to avenge Pingshu.

00:23:37.090 --> 00:23:38.290 line:80%
For my aunt?

00:23:38.290 --> 00:23:39.980 line:80%
I won't spare anyone

00:23:40.660 --> 00:23:42.610 line:80%
who wronged your aunt.

00:23:43.850 --> 00:23:45.810 line:80%
If he hadn't treated Pingshu badly,

00:23:45.810 --> 00:23:47.660 line:80%
she wouldn't have left Peiqiong Manor

00:23:48.220 --> 00:23:50.460 line:80%
and wouldn't have encountered
Mu Zhengyang's schemes.

00:23:52.370 --> 00:23:53.940 line:80%
You did this for that?

00:23:54.570 --> 00:23:55.780 line:80%
But Qi,

00:23:56.460 --> 00:23:58.500 line:80%
I didn't cancel

00:23:58.500 --> 00:23:59.610 line:80%
the betrothal.

00:24:01.020 --> 00:24:02.330 line:80%
I had feelings

00:24:03.500 --> 00:24:05.090 line:80%
for Pingshu.

00:24:05.090 --> 00:24:05.930 line:80%
I know

00:24:07.330 --> 00:24:09.370 line:80%
you marrying someone else
was Pingshu's idea.

00:24:09.810 --> 00:24:11.180 line:80%
I didn't blame you then.

00:24:11.660 --> 00:24:13.090 line:80%
But later, I realized

00:24:13.940 --> 00:24:15.610 line:80%
you hurt Pingshu's heart,

00:24:15.610 --> 00:24:17.050 line:80%
so she canceled the betrothal.

00:24:17.940 --> 00:24:19.050 line:80%
Zhao, tell me.

00:24:19.050 --> 00:24:20.020 line:80%
Should such a person

00:24:20.020 --> 00:24:21.020 line:80%
be killed?

00:24:24.890 --> 00:24:26.740 line:80%
You really are the man in black.

00:24:36.460 --> 00:24:38.570 line:80%
But what did Uncle Chang do wrong?

00:24:39.530 --> 00:24:41.290 line:80%
Why slaughter his whole clan?

00:24:41.290 --> 00:24:42.700 line:80%
Because he tried to stop me

00:24:42.700 --> 00:24:43.850 line:80%
from avenging your aunt.

00:24:44.980 --> 00:24:45.993 line:80%
Why leave him alive?

00:24:47.500 --> 00:24:50.180 line:80%
When you joined forces
to protect Luoying Valley,

00:24:51.980 --> 00:24:54.660 line:80%
you'd risk your lives for each other.

00:24:55.020 --> 00:24:56.290 line:80%
So, you also injured my father,

00:24:56.700 --> 00:24:59.370 line:80%
staged the Guangtian strife,

00:24:59.740 --> 00:25:01.290 line:80%
and killed the nuns

00:25:01.290 --> 00:25:02.370 line:80%
at Xuankong Nunnery.

00:25:03.330 --> 00:25:05.020 line:80%
Master, why did you do this?

00:25:05.510 --> 00:25:07.676 line:80%
Is it all for the Night Orchid
and the Jade Sunflower?

00:25:08.460 --> 00:25:10.020 line:80%
For practicing the Ziwei Method?

00:25:10.020 --> 00:25:11.050 line:80%
I'm doing this

00:25:13.570 --> 00:25:16.020 line:80%
to fulfill Pingshu's last wish.

00:25:16.700 --> 00:25:18.420 line:80%
Pingshu always wanted

00:25:18.420 --> 00:25:20.130 line:80%
a Jianghu filled
with chivalry and justice,

00:25:20.130 --> 00:25:22.220 line:80%
where anyone could stand up.

00:25:22.220 --> 00:25:24.500 line:80%
Once I master the Ziwei Method,

00:25:24.500 --> 00:25:26.420 line:80%
I'll kill all the hypocrites

00:25:26.420 --> 00:25:27.330 line:80%
who harmed Pingshu,

00:25:27.330 --> 00:25:29.460 line:80%
then hand over a clean Jianghu

00:25:29.460 --> 00:25:30.570 line:80%
to you,

00:25:30.570 --> 00:25:31.410 line:80%
okay?

00:25:36.780 --> 00:25:38.810 line:80%
That's not what Aunt wanted.

00:25:39.220 --> 00:25:41.530 line:80%
She died to kill Nie Hengcheng.

00:25:42.370 --> 00:25:43.496 line:80%
She wouldn't want to see you

00:25:43.507 --> 00:25:45.330 line:80%
become the second Nie Hengcheng.

00:25:45.660 --> 00:25:47.810 line:80%
I won't become the second Nie Hengcheng.

00:25:48.330 --> 00:25:49.376 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng didn't know

00:25:49.387 --> 00:25:51.020 line:80%
the final step of the Ziwei Method,

00:25:51.020 --> 00:25:51.860 line:80%
but I did.

00:25:54.700 --> 00:25:55.540 line:80%
You...

00:25:56.130 --> 00:25:56.980 line:80%
You knew?

00:25:59.890 --> 00:26:01.700 line:80%
Are you going to do this to Lingbo?

00:26:05.680 --> 00:26:06.550 line:80%
Zhao...

00:26:06.560 --> 00:26:08.780 line:80%
You killed Pingshu's best friends,

00:26:09.940 --> 00:26:13.810 line:80%
yet you claim it's to avenge her?

00:26:14.420 --> 00:26:17.090 line:80%
You're putting Pingshu on the fire.

00:26:18.220 --> 00:26:20.370 line:80%
Even if it costs my life,

00:26:21.500 --> 00:26:23.810 line:80%
I'll stop you from using Pingshu's name

00:26:24.610 --> 00:26:26.850 line:80%
to commit these cruel deeds.

00:26:26.850 --> 00:26:27.890 line:80%
Best friends?

00:26:29.090 --> 00:26:30.220 line:80%
Chang Haosheng,

00:26:30.220 --> 00:26:31.460 line:80%
Song Shijun,

00:26:31.460 --> 00:26:33.220 line:80%
and Abbess Jingyuan.

00:26:33.220 --> 00:26:35.330 line:80%
Pingshu treated them as friends,

00:26:35.330 --> 00:26:36.610 line:80%
risked her life for them,

00:26:36.610 --> 00:26:37.530 line:80%
yet what did they do?

00:26:38.460 --> 00:26:39.610 line:80%
After she died,

00:26:40.610 --> 00:26:43.220 line:80%
they hid comfortably

00:26:43.220 --> 00:26:45.130 line:80%
and never sought revenge.

00:26:45.130 --> 00:26:46.940 line:80%
You hypocrites

00:26:48.020 --> 00:26:48.940 line:80%
all deserve to die.

00:26:48.940 --> 00:26:50.180 line:80%
You're insane!

00:26:51.570 --> 00:26:52.890 line:80%
Master, no!

00:26:52.890 --> 00:26:54.340 line:80%
Zhao, go!

00:26:54.780 --> 00:26:55.850 line:80%
No one leaves.

00:26:55.850 --> 00:26:56.690 line:80%
Go!

00:26:59.810 --> 00:27:00.650 line:80%
Uncle Zhou!

00:27:09.090 --> 00:27:09.930 line:80%
Song Yuzhi!

00:27:10.460 --> 00:27:11.300 line:80%
Song Yuzhi!

00:27:12.330 --> 00:27:13.700 line:80%
Song Yuzhi, open the door!

00:27:26.500 --> 00:27:27.370 line:80%
Lingbo!

00:27:51.130 --> 00:27:51.970 line:80%
Nanny Mao?

00:27:52.370 --> 00:27:53.220 line:80%
Yes.

00:27:53.220 --> 00:27:54.370 line:80%
Go see what's happening.

00:27:54.810 --> 00:27:55.650 line:80%
It's...

00:28:18.780 --> 00:28:20.660 line:80%
It's the demonic sect's alarm bell.

00:28:21.890 --> 00:28:22.890 line:80%
Someone!

00:28:25.570 --> 00:28:26.700 line:80%
Let us out!

00:28:27.330 --> 00:28:29.050 line:80%
They drugged us heavily

00:28:30.700 --> 00:28:32.180 line:80%
to trap us.

00:28:32.180 --> 00:28:33.660 line:80%
Save your energy.

00:28:34.020 --> 00:28:34.860 line:80%
Who?

00:28:36.020 --> 00:28:38.020 line:80%
Why trap us here?

00:28:38.460 --> 00:28:39.370 line:80%
I fear it's more

00:28:42.420 --> 00:28:43.940 line:80%
than just the demonic sect.

00:29:04.460 --> 00:29:05.300 line:80%
Isn't it fun?

00:29:20.780 --> 00:29:21.940 line:80%
Greetings, Master.

00:29:22.660 --> 00:29:24.700 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)
Zhao is my personal disciple

00:29:24.700 --> 00:29:26.370 line:80%
from Luoying Valley.

00:29:26.370 --> 00:29:28.500 line:80%
Today, she officially joins us,

00:29:28.500 --> 00:29:29.610 line:80%
ranking seventh.

00:29:29.610 --> 00:29:31.500 line:80%
Congrats, Master. Congrats, Zhao.

00:29:32.130 --> 00:29:34.130 line:80%
Everyone, please guide me.

00:29:34.780 --> 00:29:36.090 line:80%
Zhao is my disciple.

00:29:36.530 --> 00:29:37.810 line:80%
I can vouch for her.

00:29:38.130 --> 00:29:39.780 line:80%
Until the truth is uncovered,

00:29:40.370 --> 00:29:41.500 line:80%
no one

00:29:42.220 --> 00:29:43.570 line:80%
may speak ill of Zhao.

00:29:44.940 --> 00:29:45.980 line:80%
In life,

00:29:46.500 --> 00:29:48.530 line:80%
there are times beyond one's control.

00:29:49.570 --> 00:29:50.940 line:80%
Only by becoming strong

00:29:51.850 --> 00:29:53.050 line:80%
can one be free.

00:30:00.020 --> 00:30:00.860 line:80%
Aunt,

00:30:02.090 --> 00:30:03.570 line:80%
what should I do?

00:30:14.480 --> 00:30:15.330 line:80%
Search!

00:30:15.330 --> 00:30:16.170 line:80%
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:30:18.570 --> 00:30:19.410 line:80%
Where is she?

00:30:20.090 --> 00:30:21.740 line:80%
Cai Zhao hid in the secret realm.

00:30:22.780 --> 00:30:24.090 line:80%
By the time we pursued her,

00:30:24.850 --> 00:30:25.890 line:80%
she was gone.

00:30:30.740 --> 00:30:31.580 line:80%
Yunke,

00:30:32.460 --> 00:30:33.810 line:80%
this can't be hidden any longer.

00:30:34.570 --> 00:30:35.460 line:80%
The sooner we act,

00:30:36.570 --> 00:30:37.570 line:80%
the better.

00:30:43.890 --> 00:30:44.730 line:80%
Understood.

00:30:45.700 --> 00:30:46.540 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:30:48.330 --> 00:30:49.530 line:80%
You arrived just in time.

00:30:49.530 --> 00:30:50.638 line:80%
Why did the alarm bell sound

00:30:50.649 --> 00:30:51.610 line:80%
for no reason?

00:30:51.610 --> 00:30:52.940 line:80%
The demonic sect attacked

00:30:52.940 --> 00:30:54.130 line:80%
and killed Lord Zhou.

00:30:55.460 --> 00:30:56.370 line:80%
How could this happen?

00:30:57.610 --> 00:30:58.500 line:80%
What about your master?

00:30:59.290 --> 00:31:00.130 line:80%
He's safe.

00:31:00.370 --> 00:31:01.460 line:80%
The invaders were repelled,

00:31:01.890 --> 00:31:03.530 line:80%
but some

00:31:04.130 --> 00:31:05.460 line:80%
may still be in the mountains.

00:31:05.850 --> 00:31:07.420 line:80%
Master instructed me to tell you

00:31:07.850 --> 00:31:09.290 line:80%
to stay here

00:31:09.660 --> 00:31:10.610 line:80%
and not go wandering.

00:31:12.610 --> 00:31:13.450 line:80%
Understood.

00:31:14.290 --> 00:31:15.130 line:80%
Where's Lingbo?

00:31:15.420 --> 00:31:16.810 line:80%
She went to see Fengchi today.

00:31:17.050 --> 00:31:18.850 line:80%
She's upset that he left to do his job

00:31:19.220 --> 00:31:21.460 line:80%
without saying goodbye,

00:31:21.850 --> 00:31:23.180 line:80%
staying inside sulking.

00:31:24.180 --> 00:31:25.020 line:80%
Lady Yin,

00:31:25.290 --> 00:31:26.130 line:80%
the two factions

00:31:27.090 --> 00:31:28.290 line:80%
may face a great battle.

00:31:28.780 --> 00:31:29.980 line:80%
You should take Lingbo

00:31:29.980 --> 00:31:31.660 line:80%
and stay at the Yin estate for a while.

00:31:32.180 --> 00:31:33.220 line:80%
Once things stabilize,

00:31:33.660 --> 00:31:34.610 line:80%
I'll bring you back.

00:31:34.980 --> 00:31:36.780 line:80%
I'm still the Lady.

00:31:37.130 --> 00:31:38.290 line:80%
In danger,

00:31:38.290 --> 00:31:40.460 line:80%
how could I abandon

00:31:40.460 --> 00:31:42.180 line:80%
your master and you?

00:31:42.780 --> 00:31:43.740 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:31:43.740 --> 00:31:45.020 line:80%
I'll be careful

00:31:45.610 --> 00:31:46.576 line:80%
and won't slow you down.

00:31:47.130 --> 00:31:47.970 line:80%
Yes,

00:31:48.570 --> 00:31:49.410 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:32:15.020 --> 00:32:15.890 line:80%
Lingbo!

00:32:17.020 --> 00:32:17.860 line:80%
Lingbo!

00:32:22.230 --> 00:32:23.090 line:80%
Make way.

00:32:23.090 --> 00:32:23.930 line:80%
I'm going out!

00:32:31.500 --> 00:32:33.050 line:80%
How dare you hit me?

00:32:33.370 --> 00:32:34.530 line:80%
Someone, help!

00:32:34.810 --> 00:32:35.890 line:80%
Help!

00:32:35.890 --> 00:32:37.180 line:80%
They hit me!

00:32:37.180 --> 00:32:38.780 line:80%
Lingbo, what's wrong?

00:32:39.370 --> 00:32:41.090 line:80%
Dalou!

00:32:41.890 --> 00:32:42.810 line:80%
He hit me.

00:32:42.810 --> 00:32:43.780 line:80%
And they.

00:32:44.130 --> 00:32:45.460 line:80%
They hit me!

00:32:46.090 --> 00:32:47.850 line:80%
I'll tell Father!

00:32:47.850 --> 00:32:49.850 line:80%
I'll make Father stand up for me!

00:32:49.850 --> 00:32:50.690 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:32:50.890 --> 00:32:52.420 line:80%
Master is dealing with the demonic sect

00:32:52.980 --> 00:32:53.980 line:80%
and can't leave.

00:32:54.660 --> 00:32:55.890 line:80%
Everyone must help.

00:32:55.890 --> 00:32:56.740 line:80%
Stop causing trouble.

00:33:00.650 --> 00:33:01.500 line:80%
No!

00:33:01.500 --> 00:33:02.880 line:80%
I want to see my father!

00:33:02.980 --> 00:33:04.180 line:80%
I want to see my father!

00:33:04.180 --> 00:33:05.020 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:33:11.020 --> 00:33:11.860 line:80%
Tell me.

00:33:12.130 --> 00:33:13.890 line:80%
Why sneak in?

00:33:14.370 --> 00:33:15.940 line:80%
You made me fight them on purpose.

00:33:16.190 --> 00:33:17.509 line:80%
Luckily, my acting is convincing.

00:33:18.180 --> 00:33:19.020 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:33:20.810 --> 00:33:21.763 line:80%
I have to take you away.

00:33:24.330 --> 00:33:25.330 line:80%
Are you crazy?

00:33:25.330 --> 00:33:26.740 line:80%
Why should I leave my home

00:33:26.740 --> 00:33:28.050 line:80%
with a demoness like you?

00:33:29.180 --> 00:33:30.020 line:80%
Zhao,

00:33:30.530 --> 00:33:31.850 line:80%
do you know something?

00:33:39.220 --> 00:33:41.820 line:80%
(Discipline Hall)

00:34:08.890 --> 00:34:09.730 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:34:10.850 --> 00:34:11.740 line:80%
are you alright?

00:34:13.100 --> 00:34:13.970 line:80%
Master,

00:34:15.850 --> 00:34:17.890 line:80%
Zhao will stop you.

00:34:18.220 --> 00:34:19.890 line:80%
Why?

00:34:21.810 --> 00:34:22.650 line:80%
Tell me.

00:34:23.660 --> 00:34:24.810 line:80%
Don't you want

00:34:24.810 --> 00:34:26.850 line:80%
a clean Jianghu?

00:34:26.850 --> 00:34:29.290 line:80%
A Jianghu won through killing

00:34:29.930 --> 00:34:31.450 line:80%
can't be clean.

00:34:31.700 --> 00:34:32.890 line:80%
This Jianghu

00:34:33.490 --> 00:34:35.330 line:80%
is already rotten.

00:34:37.180 --> 00:34:38.370 line:80%
Pingshu said

00:34:39.780 --> 00:34:40.890 line:80%
that for over 200 years,

00:34:41.780 --> 00:34:42.890 line:80%
the Six Sects

00:34:43.450 --> 00:34:45.450 line:80%
had grown stagnant,

00:34:45.450 --> 00:34:46.890 line:80%
stuck in old ways.

00:34:47.290 --> 00:34:48.740 line:80%
Many ambitious youths,

00:34:49.700 --> 00:34:51.370 line:80%
born into low status,

00:34:51.850 --> 00:34:53.810 line:80%
couldn't rise

00:34:53.810 --> 00:34:55.410 line:80%
and were suppressed.

00:34:55.930 --> 00:34:57.290 line:80%
Shouldn't this Jianghu

00:34:58.490 --> 00:35:00.010 line:80%
change?

00:35:00.010 --> 00:35:01.330 line:80%
You mean

00:35:03.180 --> 00:35:05.620 line:80%
by killing them all?

00:35:05.620 --> 00:35:06.460 line:80%
Yes.

00:35:08.370 --> 00:35:09.370 line:80%
Break to build.

00:35:10.450 --> 00:35:12.180 line:80%
From ruin to renewal.

00:35:12.180 --> 00:35:13.970 line:80%
Taichu Temple is gone;

00:35:13.970 --> 00:35:16.010 line:80%
Siqi Sect is nearly destroyed.

00:35:16.010 --> 00:35:18.290 line:80%
Chaos at Peiqiong Manor is imminent.

00:35:18.290 --> 00:35:20.140 line:80%
Guangtian Sect can't be left behind.

00:35:20.810 --> 00:35:22.010 line:80%
Luoying Valley

00:35:22.930 --> 00:35:24.970 line:80%
has always lived in seclusion.

00:35:25.410 --> 00:35:27.540 line:80%
I'll leave Qingque Sect.

00:35:28.010 --> 00:35:28.850 line:80%
Then,

00:35:29.290 --> 00:35:31.060 line:80%
the Six Sects combined

00:35:31.060 --> 00:35:32.490 line:80%
will be handed to you and Zhao.

00:35:32.490 --> 00:35:33.330 line:80%
Agreed?

00:35:33.330 --> 00:35:34.780 line:80%
You've done so many evil deeds.

00:35:35.450 --> 00:35:37.970 line:80%
How will Jianghu see our sect?

00:35:37.970 --> 00:35:38.810 line:80%
Easy.

00:35:40.660 --> 00:35:41.660 line:80%
Once I clear

00:35:42.140 --> 00:35:43.850 line:80%
all obstacles,

00:35:44.410 --> 00:35:45.540 line:80%
take my head

00:35:46.330 --> 00:35:48.100 line:80%
to honor the dead,

00:35:48.100 --> 00:35:49.220 line:80%
and use my blood

00:35:49.970 --> 00:35:51.740 line:80%
to cleanse the sect's shame.

00:35:52.370 --> 00:35:53.210 line:80%
Let me

00:35:53.810 --> 00:35:54.850 line:80%
be infamous forever.

00:35:55.220 --> 00:35:56.140 line:80%
Only then

00:35:57.140 --> 00:35:58.780 line:80%
will Jianghu submit to you.

00:35:58.780 --> 00:35:59.630 line:80%
No.

00:35:59.640 --> 00:36:01.060 line:80%
We don't want this Jianghu.

00:36:01.060 --> 00:36:02.450 line:80%
I only want my old master.

00:36:03.060 --> 00:36:04.490 line:80%
Master, do you remember?

00:36:04.970 --> 00:36:07.140 line:80%
When I joined, you warned me

00:36:08.010 --> 00:36:09.490 line:80%
not to fear the strong,

00:36:09.970 --> 00:36:10.890 line:80%
not to bully the weak,

00:36:11.279 --> 00:36:13.292 line:80%
not to kill recklessly,
and not to act arrogantly.

00:36:13.410 --> 00:36:14.290 line:80%
My master

00:36:14.290 --> 00:36:15.620 line:80%
would never kill my father,

00:36:16.060 --> 00:36:18.220 line:80%
nor Mr. Chang or Lord Zhou.

00:36:18.850 --> 00:36:20.410 line:80%
It's not too late.

00:36:21.180 --> 00:36:22.220 line:80%
Please stop, Master.

00:36:22.220 --> 00:36:23.620 line:80%
Stop, Master.

00:36:30.970 --> 00:36:31.850 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:36:33.060 --> 00:36:34.330 line:80%
you haven't failed

00:36:34.330 --> 00:36:36.290 line:80%
all these years of my guidance.

00:36:36.700 --> 00:36:38.100 line:80%
You haven't disappointed me.

00:36:39.620 --> 00:36:40.740 line:80%
I'm at ease.

00:36:42.060 --> 00:36:42.900 line:80%
Master...

00:36:44.370 --> 00:36:45.210 line:80%
Master...

00:36:45.490 --> 00:36:46.930 line:80%
I beg you to stop, Master.

00:36:47.580 --> 00:36:48.420 line:80%
Master...

00:36:49.890 --> 00:36:51.540 line:80%
Master!

00:37:00.361 --> 00:37:11.021 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:37:29.781 --> 00:37:34.191 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:37:34.756 --> 00:37:39.371 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:37:39.711 --> 00:37:44.276 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:37:44.801 --> 00:37:49.101 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:37:52.046 --> 00:37:56.746 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:37:57.271 --> 00:38:01.561 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:38:02.221 --> 00:38:06.251 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:38:06.566 --> 00:38:11.691 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:38:12.266 --> 00:38:17.076 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:17.291 --> 00:38:21.461 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:22.186 --> 00:38:26.121 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:38:26.621 --> 00:38:31.896 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:38:54.626 --> 00:38:59.756 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:00.121 --> 00:39:04.491 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:04.756 --> 00:39:08.886 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:09.071 --> 00:39:14.646 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪